{"type":"article","id":12660,"title":"疫情阴影下的人性 —— 武汉肺炎患者自救故事一两则","uid":7997,"topics":[5262,1133],"contents":"<blockquote>⚠注意：本文消息汇总自中文社交媒体，未经FC，在可预见的未来也不会有官方出面FC，相关资讯真实性还请广大葱油自我判断。</blockquote><br>\n1. 武汉儿童出现冠状肺炎症状，救子心切的家长驱车千里自驾拉到上海复旦儿科（可以理解），造成“复旦儿科全院戒备”，遭到上海宝妈们责备（也可以理解）<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/hP1lwWY.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/hP1lwWY.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/hP1lwWY.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/1eJ2Wkt.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1eJ2Wkt.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/1eJ2Wkt.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/0Pym7QH.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0Pym7QH.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/0Pym7QH.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/b7tTFpH.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/b7tTFpH.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/b7tTFpH.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n2. 青岛零号病人来自武汉，在日照自觉身体不适便雇用了一辆<b>空客车</b>，自己坐在<b>最后排</b>，一路开到青岛这边名气最大的医院，进门自报情况。司机疑似被传染。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/9a0lEnN.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9a0lEnN.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/9a0lEnN.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/FZWEK0P.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FZWEK0P.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/FZWEK0P.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-01-23","agreeCount":2,"discussionCount":0}